<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Rosedale</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Down 16th Ave west is North Hill Centre, a small mall with over 100 stores and 2 major anchors, a Sears and a Safeway. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Rosedale is adjacent to ACAD and SAIT Polytechnic, where the nearest C-train station is located, providing quick and easy transport to the downtown core for daily commuters. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Located in nearby Hillhurst is Riley Park and Burns Memorial Park, great places to enjoy the outdoors.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The CBE operates a elementary/junior high school in the area.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Rosedale is located near Foothills Hospital, with medical clinics including dentists and family doctors operating in nearby Kensington BRZ. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">C-train access is available via SAIT/ACAD/Jubilee station. Rosedale is located in Ward 7 of the Calgary City Council.</p>


